Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C). Grease and flour a 5x9-inch loaf pan. Mash bananas and add flour, sugar, butter, vanilla, baking powder, baking soda and egg. Mix well. Pour into loaf pan. Bake in preheated oven until toothpick inserted into center of cake comes out clean, 50 to 60 minutes.